OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773765957
OL,3,CPublic to decide which artist should
OL,4,Ccreate work from Sycamore Gap tree wood
OL,6,FAlso put forward are nationwide
OL,7,Fparticipatory projects that gather
OL,8,Fpersonal stories, distribute symbolic
OL,9,Fcarved seeds, build platforms for
OL,10,Fconversations about climate or bring
OL,11,Fcommunities together in song and
OL,12,Fremembrance.
OL,14,FThe six shortlisted artists or
OL,15,Fcollaborations are:
OL,17,FAlex Hartley and Tom James, based in
OL,18,FDevon & London ` Viewpoint
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
