OL,6,FHelix Arts x George King Architects,
OL,7,Fbased in the North East ` The People's
OL,8,FTree, A Shared Story
OL,10,FMary Dalton, based in Hampshire `
OL,11,FSycamore Gap Black
OL,13,Fnon zero one, based in London ` SEEDS
OL,15,FSam Williams Studio, based in Sussex `
OL,16,FStories of 1000 trees
OL,18,FTrigger, based in Bristol ` Twirl
