OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773765957
OL,3,CPublic to decide which artist should
OL,4,Ccreate work from Sycamore Gap tree wood
OL,6,FThe wood is now ready for artists to
OL,7,Fwork with after being stored to season
OL,8,Fover the past 28 months.
OL,10,FThe winner will be announced later in
OL,11,Fthe spring and the final artwork is
OL,12,Fexpected to be completed by 2028.
OL,14,FIt comes more than two years after
OL,15,FDaniel Graham and Adam Carruthers,
OL,16,Ffrom Cumbria, travelled to Hadrian's
OL,17,FWall in Northumberland during Storm
OL,18,FAgnes in 2023 to cut down the world-
OL,19,Ffamous tree, which is thought to have
OL,20,Fbeen planted in the late 1880s.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
