PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773765957
OL,3,CPublic to decide which artist should
OL,4,Ccreate work from Sycamore Gap tree wood
OL,6,FThe act of vandalism sparked national
OL,7,Foutrage and an outpouring of grief for
OL,8,Fthe widely loved landmark.
OL,10,FAnnie Reilly, National Trust public
OL,11,Fengagement director and chairwoman of
OL,12,Fthe judging panel, said: "Over the
OL,13,Fpast two years, we've heard
OL,14,Fextraordinary stories about what the
OL,15,FSycamore Gap tree meant to people `
OL,16,Ffrom moments of celebration and
OL,17,Fmilestones to quiet memories of loss,
OL,18,Fconnection and reflection.
OL,26,@tD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
