PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773765957
OL,3,CPublic to decide which artist should
OL,4,Ccreate work from Sycamore Gap tree wood
OL,6,F"We're proud to support this
OL,7,Fcommission, which ensures that this
OL,8,Fdeeply loved landmark continues to
OL,9,Finspire creativity and reflection.
OL,11,F"The shortlisted artists bring
OL,12,Fexceptional imagination, sensitivity
OL,13,Fand skill. Each offers a unique way of
OL,14,Fhonouring the tree's loss while
OL,15,Fcelebrating its enduring place in our
OL,16,Fshared cultural memory."
OL,18,FPeople can cast up to three votes
OL,19,Fusing a valid email address at
OL,20,Fwww.nationaltrust.org.uk/sycamore-gap-
OL,21,Fcommission.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@XO]
